rComments: He is a hard worker and it shows. If you put in the effort and work hard too, you'll get a good grade. He's a reasonable person. A little hard but just work harder.
This is a hard course with a lot of things to study for the mid-term and the final exam.  The tutorials are time consuming and there are many formulas to know in order to do the assignment.

Dr Greenwood is friendly and helpful. He presents the material in a well organized manner. The mid- term is hard, but Dr Greenwood marks it fairly. The labs are time consuming and not very interesting. He reminds me of Santa clause.
